Identify {= retailer =}+ online houseplant or home-garden plant retailers; cover the {= evidence_facet =} evidence facets listed below for each retailer by supplying a source (i.e. {= url =}+ URL per facet) which exposes a focused, substantive, source-bounded capability finding clearly scoped to the facet in question. Each retailer should sell live houseplants, rare or tropical collector plants, succulents or cacti, outdoor garden plants, seeds, shrubs, perennials, or comparable home-garden plant goods through an online catalog, shop, or order flow.

